    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="original">
                <pb facs="EHRI-ET-WL05320102_01.jpg" n="1"/>
                <p>פּראָטאָקאָל נומער 102</p>
                <p>דעם 2־טן יאַנואַר <date when="1940-01-01">1940</date></p>
                <p><persName ref="#ehri_et_r_avrom" type="ehri">אבֿרהם ר.</persName></p>
                <p>20 יאָר אַלט</p>
                <p>שניטער פֿון <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">לאָמזשע</placeName></p>
                <p>איצט – <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">װילנע</placeName></p>
                <p>פֿון <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans" type="subject">דײַטשע</term> אַעראָפּלאַנען 2 באָמבאַרדירונגען ערבֿ ראָש־השנה איז
                    אין <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">לאָמזשע</placeName>
                    <term ref="#t536" type="subject">דערהרגעט</term> געװאָרן <persName ref="#ehri_et_markevitsh" type="ehri">מאַרקעװיטש</persName> –
                    אַ שרײַבער אין <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">מאַגיסטראַט</placeName>.</p>
                <p>מיך האָבן די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans" type="subject">דײַטשן</term> פֿאַרנומען אין אַ <placeName ref="#l1178"
                        type="camp">געפֿאַנגען־לאַגער קײן ראַסטענבורג</placeName>. דאָרט זענען געװען 13 הונדערט ייִדן. מ'האָט אונדז נישט געגעבן קײן
                        <term ref="#t832" type="subject">עסן</term>. יעדן פֿאַרנאַכט האָט מען געגעבן אַ לעבל <term ref="#t832" type="subject"
                        >ברויט</term> אויף 4 מענטשן, און דאָס איז געװען דאָס גאַנצע <term ref="#t832" type="subject">עסן</term>.</p>
                <p>אײנמאָל זענען געקומען <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_poles" type="subject">פּוילישע</term>
                    <term ref="#t669" type="subject">געפֿאַנגענע</term>. די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans" type="subject">דײַטשן</term>
                    האָבן זײ געהײסן אונדז אויסטאָן אַלע <term ref="#t836" type="subject">מלבושים</term>. זײ האָבן טאַקע אונדז אויסגעטאָן ביז נאַקעט
                    און אַלץ צוגענומען פֿאַר זיך.</p>
                <p>פֿאַר מײַן צײַט אין <placeName ref="#l1178" type="camp">לאַגער</placeName> – 3 װאָכן – <term ref="#t536" type="subject">זענען
                        געשטאָרבן</term> 3 ייִדן, װאָס האָבן נישט געקענט איבערהאַלטן דעם <term ref="#t569" type="subject">הונגער</term>, די <term
                        ref="#t831" type="subject">קעלט</term> און די קלעפּ.</p>
                <p>דעם צװײטן טאָג סוכּות זענען באַפֿרײַט געװאָרן פֿון <placeName ref="#l1178" type="camp">לאַגער</placeName> טויזנט <term ref="#t826"
                        type="subject">מען</term>, װעלכע מען האָט געהײסן גײן צו די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets" type="subject"
                        >סאָװיעטישע</term> געביטן. איך בין אויך געװאָרן באַפֿרײַט. <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">לאָמזשע</placeName> איז
                    איבערגעגאַנגען צו די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets" type="subject">סאָװיעטן</term>.</p>
                <p>איך בין אַװעק קײן <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">װילנע</placeName>, װײַל אין אַמעריקע האָב איך אַ <term ref="#t822"
                        type="subject">ברודער</term> און איך װיל צו אים פֿאָרן.</p>
                <p>אונטערגעשריבן: <persName ref="#ehri_et_r_avrom" type="ehri">אבֿרהם ר.</persName></p>
            </div>
            <div type="transcription">
                <pb facs="EHRI-ET-WL05320102_01.jpg" n="1"/>
                <p>Protocol No. 102</p>
                <p><date when="1940-01-02">2 January 1940</date></p>
                <p><persName ref="#ehri_et_r_avrom" type="ehri">Avrom R.</persName></p>
                <p>20-years old</p>
                <p>Harvester from <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">Łomża</placeName></p>
                <p>Now – <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">Vilnius</placeName></p>
                <p>From <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">German</term> airplanes during 2 bombardments on the eve of Rosh Hashanah in
                        <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">Łomża</placeName>, <persName ref="#ehri_et_markevitsh" type="ehri">Markevitsh</persName>
                    was <term ref="#t536" type="subject">killed</term> – a writer in the <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">city
                    hall</placeName>.</p>
                <p>I was detained by the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> in a <placeName ref="#l1178" type="camp">prison
                        camp close to Rastenburg [Kętrzyn]</placeName>. There were 13 hundred Jews there. They did not give us <term ref="#t832"
                        type="subject">food</term>. Every evening, they gave one loaf of <term ref="#t832" type="subject">bread</term> to be shared by
                    4 persons, and this was all we had to <term ref="#t832" type="subject">eat</term>.</p>
                <p>Once <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_poles">Polish</term>
                    <term ref="#t669" type="subject">prisoners</term> arrived. The <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> ordered
                    them to take off all our <term ref="#t836" type="subject">clothes</term>. They indeed undressed us until we were naked and took
                    all of it for themselves.</p>
                <p>During my time in the <placeName ref="#l1178" type="camp">camp</placeName> – 3 weeks –, 3 <term ref="#t536" type="subject">Jews
                        died</term> who could not endure the <term ref="#t569" type="subject">hunger</term>, the <term ref="#t831" type="subject"
                        >cold</term> and the beatings anymore.</p>
                <p>On the second day of Sukkot, a thousand <term ref="#t826" type="subject">men</term> were released from the <placeName ref="#l1178"
                        type="camp">camp</placeName> who were ordered to go to the <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets">Soviet</term>
                    territories. I was also released. <placeName ref="#lomza" type="ehri">Łomża</placeName> was transferred to the <term
                        ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_soviets">Soviets</term>.</p>
                <p>I left for <placeName ref="#vilnius" type="ehri">Vilnius</placeName> because I have a <term ref="#t822" type="subject"
                        >brother</term> in America and I want to go to him.</p>
                <p>Signed: <persName ref="#ehri_et_r_avrom" type="ehri">Avrom R.</persName></p>
            </div>
        </body>
